is a Japanese manga series written and illustrated by Bomhat. It was serialized in Kodansha's  manga magazine Monthly Afternoon from December 2022 to January 2025, with its chapters collected in five  volumes.
Publication
Written and illustrated by Bomhat, A Kingdom of Quartz was serialized in Kodansha's  manga magazine Monthly Afternoon from December 22, 2022, to January 24, 2025. Kodansha collected its chapters in five  volumes, released from May 23, 2023, to April 23, 2025.
In North America, the manga is licensed for English release by Kodansha USA.
